name: The Ancient of Days NFT Tracker
description: Custom tracker for all activity relating to The Ancient of Days NFT. The series of 50 NFTs was first sold in July 2021 by the Whitworth, The University of Manchester, in partnership with Vastari Labs (https://twitter.com/vastari_labs). The tracker is due to form part of the 'Economics The Blockbuster' exhibition, planned to take place in 2023.
